MODEL ATMOSPHERE FILES TO BE USED WITH SIR

Each model file contains the macroturbulent velocity (km/s), the
filling factor (only to be used with two-component models, ranging
from 0 to 1), and the stray light factor (in percent) in the first line.
Then, eight columns follow:
 
Column 1: log tau_5 (logarithm of the continuum optical depth at 5000 A)
Column 2: Temperature (K)
Column 3: Electron pressures (dyn/cm^2)
Column 4: Microturbulent velocity (cm/s)
Column 5: Magnetic field strength (G)
Column 6: Line-of-sight velocity (cm/s)
Column 7: Inclination angle of the magnetic field vector in deg 
          from 0 (pointing to the observer) to 180 (pointing away from the
          observer)
Column 8: Azimuthal angle of the magnetic field vector in deg. 

Note that electron pressure comes from hydrostatic equilibrium, and that
microturbulent velocities are set to reasonable values (usually not given in 
the original sources). Macroturbulence is seldomly given in the original
sources (except for those models originating from the IAC inversion group).
 

References for the models are as follow: 

One-component quiet Sun models:

  holmu0.mod ...  Holweger H., & Muller E.A., 1974, Sol Phys. 39 19

  hsra.mod   ...  Harvard Smithsonian Reference Atmosphere (Gingerich O.,
                  Noyes R.W., Kalkofen W., & Cuny Y., 1971. Sol. Phys. 18, 347)

  valc.mod   ...  Vernaza J.E., Avrett E.H., & Loeser R., 1981, ApJS 45, 635

  mackkl.mod ...  Maltby P., Avrett E.H., Carlsson M., Kjeldseth-Moe O.,
                  Kurucz R.L., & Loeser R., 1986 ApJ 306 284

  nelsoncold.mod  Nelson G. P. 1978 Sol. Phys. 60, 5

  nelsonhot.mod   Nelson G. P. 1978 Sol. Phys. 60, 5

  grevesse.mod .. Grevesse N., Sauval A.J. 1999 A&A 347, 348


Two-component (granular and intergranular) models of the quiet Sun:


  granulebbr.mod .. Borrero, J.M., \& Bellot Rubio, 2002, A\&A, 385, 1056
  intergrbbr.mod .. Borrero, J.M., \& Bellot Rubio, 2002, A\&A, 385, 1056 


  granulebrc.mod ...  B. Ruiz Cobo, J.C. del Toro Iniesta, I. Rodr\'\i guez 
                   Hidalgo, M. Collados \& J. S\'anchez Almeida;  JOSO Annual 
                   Report, 162 (1995)

  intergrbrc.mod ...  B. Ruiz Cobo, J.C. del Toro Iniesta, I. Rodr\'\i guez 
                   Hidalgo, M. Collados \& J. S\'anchez Almeida;  JOSO Annual 
                   Report, 162 (1995)
  

Sunspot Models:

  emaltby.mod .. (E model) Maltby P., Avrett E.H., Carlsson M., 
                  Kjeldseth-Moe O., Kurucz R.L., & Loeser R., 1986 ApJ 306 284
                 
  mmaltby.mod ..  (M model) Maltby P., Avrett E.H., Carlsson M., 
                  Kjeldseth-Moe O., Kurucz R.L., & Loeser R., 1986 ApJ 306 284
                 

  cool.mod ...    Collados M., Martínez Pillet V., Ruiz Cobo B., 
                  Del Toro Iniesta J.C., & Vázquez M. 1994 A&A 291 622 
                  (Umbral model for a big spot)

  hot.mod  ...    Collados M., Martínez Pillet V., Ruiz Cobo B., 
                  Del Toro Iniesta J.C., & Vázquez M. 1994 A&A 291 622 
		  (Umbral model for a small spot)

  penumjti.mod .. Del Toro Iniesta J.C., Tarbell T.D., Ruiz Cobo B., 
                   1994, ApJ 436,400 
		  (penumbral model)

Active Regions Models:

  solannt.mod ..  (network model, S. K. Solanki, private comunication)

  solanpl.mod ..  (plage model, S. K. Solanki, private comunication)




